<span id="freeTextContainer14035762687218417450">This is a great P&amp;P variation. Highly recommend. Great plot twist, ample misunderstandings for D &amp; E to suffer through. Then Darcy knocks Wickham out cold... what more could you want? They even pull one over on Lady C. (which is a nice change as I was getting tired of reading her rantings in other P&amp;P variations). Happy endings all around with a neat little epilogue to tie up the loose ends. Makes me smile :)<br/>Read: July 9, 2014<br/>Read: March 25, 2015</span>

          </span>
